  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Reducing the time patients spend in the labor and delivery room saves money and reduces
      patient discomfort as well and reducing complications. We will compare two methods for
      inducing cervical maturation in order to shorten the time taken between administration of
      drugs and delivery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
